title: Wall Street Breakfast August 10: Consumer Price Inflation Seen Easing in July, but Pressures Still Persist
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Consumer price inflation seen easing in July, but pressures still persist. Justice Dept. could sue Google over ad dominance as soon as September - Bloomberg. Elon Musk backtracks on stock pledge, sells $7B of Tesla before Twitter court fight. Catch today’s WSB article here.
